                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#146r">Fol. 146r</locus>: Regulation concerning the use of land, established by the people and clergy of Dǝbla Däbrä Bǝrhan Yoḥannǝs Mätmǝq in 1939 E.C. (= 1947 A.D.).<q xml:lang="gez"/>
