                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a7">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <desc>Fol.  147r: Donation note.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol.  147r: ዝወንጌል፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡ ደብላ፡ ብላታ፡ ገብረ፡ ሕይወት፡ ዘፈሃቃ፡ ወዘሰረቃ፡ ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ወጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በአፈ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ኢትርስኡኒ፡ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ለዓለመ፡  ዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol.  147r: This (is) the Gospel which blatta<i> </i>Gäbrä Ḥǝywät donated to (the church of) Yoḥannǝs Däbla. May the one who erased and stole this book be excommunicated through the mouth of Peter and Paul. May you not forget (to recite) Pater Noster for my sake! For eternity. Amen. </q>
                           
                        </item>
